Sentencas: In this study, SrCo1-ySbyO3-delta powders were prepared by a modified Pechini method.
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: According to the study results, the cubic Pm3m phase of the SrCo1-ySbyO3-delta ceramics was obtained as 10% of cobalt ions were substituted by antimony ions.
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Doping of Sb3+ ions appeared both to stabilize the Pm3m phase of the SrCo1-ySbyO3-delta ceramics and to enhance densification and retard grain growth.
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The coefficient of thermal expansion of the SrCo1-xSbxO3-delta ceramics increased with the content of the antimony ions, ranging from 10.17 to 15.37 ppm/degrees C at temperatures lower than the inflection point (ranging from 450 degrees C to 550 degrees C) and from 22.16 to 29.29 ppm/degrees C at higher temperatures.
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: For the SrCo0.98Sb0.02O3-delta ceramic, electrical conductivity reached a maximum of 507 S/cm at 450 degrees C.
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The ohmic and polarization resistances of the single cell with the pure SrCo0.98Sb0.02O3-delta cathode at 700 degrees C read respectively 0.298 Omega cm(2) and 0.560 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The single cell with the SrCo0.98Sb0.02O3-delta-SDC composite cathode appeared to reduce the impedances with the R-0 and R-p at 700 degrees C reading respectively 0.109
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications
SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Without microstructure optimization and measured at 700 degrees C, the single cells with the pure SrCo0.98Sb0.02O3-delta cathode and the SrCo0.98Sb0.02O3-delta-SDC composite cathode, demonstrated maximum power densities of 0.100 W/cm(2) and 0.487 W/cm(2).
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Apparently, SrCo1-ySbyO3-delta is a potential cathode for use in IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: SrCo1-xSbxO3-δ cathode materials prepared by Pechini method for solid oxide fuel cell applications
